quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  65,8,"How many a city has turned away from the bidding of its Lord and His apostles; and we called them to a severe account, and we tormented them with an unheard-of torment"
  65,9,And they tasted the evil results of their conduct; and the end of their conduct was loss
  65,10,"God prepared for them severe torment;- then fear God, ye who are endowed with minds"
  65,11,"Ye who believe! God has sent down to you a reminder; - an apostle to recite to you God's manifest signs;- to bring forth those who believe and act aright from darkness into light! and whoso believes in God and acts right He will bring him into gardens beneath which rivers flow, to dwell therein for ever and for aye! God has made goodly for him his provision"
  65,12,"God it is who created seven heavens, and of the earth the like thereof. The bidding descends between them, that ye may know that God is mighty over all, and that God has encompassed all things with His knowledge"